<h3 id="measure-of-unit-quality">Measure of Unit Quality</h3>

<p>Lratio &amp; Isolation Distance</p>

<p><em>problem: normality is assumed.</em></p>

<h3 id="sorting-bias--confounds">Sorting Bias &amp; Confounds</h3>

<ul>
  <li>neuron bursting</li>
  <li>waveform overlaps of near-synchronous spikes</li>
  <li>back-propagation of dendritic action potentials</li>
  <li>time-delayed action potentials</li>
  <li>electrode drift</li>
  <li>biophysiological difference across brain regions</li>
</ul>

